item.title: Watchlog
item.description: 2020 The Perks of Being a Wallflower (2012) (x2) This is one cheeky, moving and relevant coming-of-age movie that every teenager should watch atleast once. I am personally indebted to this movie for introducing me to the ethereal Cocteau Twins. Spider-Man Far from Home (2019) (x1) Yea, I enjoy Marvel when I lose my sense of purpose in life and love to squander my time at things less important than planning the next rebellion.
